comments: Created 1.4.2007 out of the Torbay unparished area.

Created 1.4.1968 out of the parishes of Brixham, Churston Ferrers, 
    Coffinswell, Kerswells, Marldon, Paignton, torquay. Abolished 1.4.1974 to become 
    an unparished area. See also Table 2, notes (a) and (b).
Unparished area which until 1.4.1974 formed the parish of Torbay.
